Djokovic’s U.S. Open Victory Over Nadal Draws 18% Higher TV Rating for CBS

-- B y   E b e n   N o v y - W i l l i a m s
-- 
2011-09-13T15:40:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-13/djokovic-s-u-s-open-victory-over-nadal-draws-18-higher-tv-rating-for-cbs.html
Novak Djokovic’s four-set win over
 Rafael Nadal  in the U.S. Open tennis men’s final yesterday drew
18 percent higher television ratings for CBS in the nation’s
biggest markets, CBS Inc. spokesman Jerry Caraccioli said in a
telephone interview.  The match drew a 2.6 rating, up from a 2.2 last year when
the same two players met in a Monday final.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Eben Novywilliams in New York at 
 enovywilliam@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Michael Sillup at 
 msillup@bloomberg.net  